public static class SheetEvent.CellStyleChanged extends SheetEvent.CellChanged<Object> implements SheetEvent
Event class representing a change in a cell's style within a sheet.

This class extends SheetEvent.CellChanged to include details about the cell whose style has changed. It implements the SheetEvent interface to indicate it is a type of sheet event.
